This paper is primarily focused on image recognition using deep neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the optimization and training of these networks, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of residual networks and their improved performance is related to neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM).
